{"slug":"sirkuler-26-0274","reference":"Sirkuler_26_0274","gazette":"06 Mayıs 2026 Tarihli ve 33245 Sayılı Resmî Gazete","title":"Kosova Menşeli Sentetik Filament Dokuma Mensucat İthalatına Yönelik Önlemlerin Etkisiz Kılınması Soruşturması Açıldı","date":"06 Mayıs 2026","bodyHtml":"<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Ticaret Bakanlığı tarafından yayımlanan\r\n“İthalatta Haksız Rekabetin Önlenmesine İlişkin Tebliğ (Tebliğ No: 2026/14)”\r\nile, Kosova Cumhuriyeti menşeli/çıkışlı 54.07 GTP altında sınıflandırılan\r\n“sentetik filament iplikten dokunmuş mensucat (giyim için olanlar)” ithalatına\r\nyönelik önlemlerin etkisiz kılındığı iddiası kapsamında resen soruşturma\r\naçılmıştır.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Söz konusu düzenleme kapsamında öne çıkan\r\nhususlar aşağıda yer almaktadır:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Soruşturma;\r\nÇin Halk Cumhuriyeti (ÇHC) menşeli eşya için halen yürürlükte bulunan damping\r\nönlemlerinin, Kosova üzerinden gerçekleştirilen ithalat yoluyla etkisiz kılınıp\r\nkılınmadığının tespitine yöneliktir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">İnceleme\r\nkonusu eşya, 54.07 GTP altında yer alan ve Ek-1’de GTİP’leri belirtilen\r\n“sentetik filament iplikten dokunmuş mensucat (giyim için olanlar)” ürünlerini\r\nkapsamaktadır. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Tebliğde yer\r\nverilen verilere göre; <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Kosova’dan ithalat miktarı 2023 yılında 23,4\r\nton iken, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">2024 yılında 398 tona, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">2025 yılında ise 1.112 tona yükselmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Kosova\r\nmenşeli ithalatın birim fiyatlarının, ÇHC menşeli ürünlerin birim fiyatlarına\r\nyakın seviyelerde gerçekleştiği belirtilmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">İthalatta\r\nHaksız Rekabeti Değerlendirme Kurulu tarafından; <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Yönetmeliğin 38 inci maddesi kapsamında\r\nönlemlerin etkisiz kılınmasına karşı soruşturma açılmasına, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:72.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Ayrıca Kosova menşeli/çıkışlı ithalatın, ÇHC\r\nmenşeli eşya için uygulanmakta olan damping önlemi tutarında teminata\r\nbağlanmasına karar verilmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Soruşturma\r\nTicaret Bakanlığı İthalat Genel Müdürlüğü tarafından yürütülecektir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:7.3pt;margin-bottom:\r\n0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\nSymbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">İlgili\r\ntarafların soru formunu cevaplandırma süresi; bildirimin gönderildiği tarihten\r\nveya Tebliğin yayım tarihinden itibaren posta süresi dahil 37 gün olarak\r\nbelirlenmiştir. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;\">Tebliğ yayımı tarihinde yürürlüğe girmiştir.</span></p><p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-right:7.3pt;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Kaynak\r\n:</span> <a href=\"https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2026/05/20260506-3.htm\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2026/05/20260506-3.htm</a></p>\n                                <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-danger\" href=\"\">\n                                    \n                                </a>"}
